    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn3.16:1.1",
          "pli": "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. ",
          "en": "At Sāvatthī. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn3.16:1.2",
          "pli": "Atha kho rājā pasenadi kosalo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. ",
          "en": "Then King Pasenadi of Kosala went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one side. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn3.16:1.3",
          "pli": "Atha kho aññataro puriso yena rājā pasenadi kosalo tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā rañño pasenadissa kosalassa upakaṇṇake ārocesi: ",
          "en": "Then a man went up to the king and whispered in his ear, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn3.16:1.4",
          "pli": "“mallikā, deva, devī dhītaraṃ vijātā”ti. ",
          "en": "“Your Majesty, Queen Mallikā has given birth to a daughter.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn3.16:1.5",
          "pli": "Evaṃ vutte, rājā pasenadi kosalo anattamano ahosi. ",
          "en": "When this was said, King Pasenadi was disappointed. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn3.16:2.1",
          "pli": "Atha kho bhagavā rājānaṃ pasenadiṃ kosalaṃ anattamanataṃ viditvā tāyaṃ velāyaṃ imā gāthāyo abhāsi: ",
          "en": "Then, knowing that King Pasenadi was disappointed, on that occasion the Buddha recited these verses: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn3.16:3.1",
          "pli": "“Itthīpi hi ekacciyā, ",
          "en": "“Well, some women are better than men, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn3.16:3.2",
          "pli": "seyyā posa janādhipa; ",
          "en": "O ruler of the people. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn3.16:3.3",
          "pli": "Medhāvinī sīlavatī, ",
          "en": "Wise and virtuous, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn3.16:3.4",
          "pli": "sassudevā patibbatā. ",
          "en": "a devoted wife who honors her mother in law. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn3.16:4.1",
          "pli": "Tassā yo jāyati poso, ",
          "en": "And when she has a son, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn3.16:4.2",
          "pli": "sūro hoti disampati; ",
          "en": "he becomes a hero, O lord of the land. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn3.16:4.3",
          "pli": "Tādisā subhagiyā putto, ",
          "en": "The son of such a blessed lady "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn3.16:4.4",
          "pli": "rajjampi anusāsatī”ti. ",
          "en": "may even rule the realm.”"
        }
      ],
